{"tid":1816903,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"同我入晒嚟 杜文澤Late show 2020香港啟示錄已中兩樣","createTime":"2020-01-08T15:32:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T16:56:07.000Z","uid":42281,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e7f05b96d9c11558bd21b408981bda158fdb8475","tid":1816903,"uid":42281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:32:38.000Z","msg":"有時真係唔到你唔信<br />\n<br />\n第一：<br />\n片入面占卜提到嘅手足之間會出現分歧<br />\n呢個一入2020已經中咗<br />\n和理非捉鬼捉上腦 令到好多勇武手足好失望<br />\n同時令到好多手足失去士氣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二：<br />\n占卜入面都有提到有一部份嘅手足會想退出/離開香港<br />\n近日已經有前線手兄出post講退隊嘅事<br />\n同時已經有手兄俾人當鬼捉最後要離開香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n解決方法：<br />\n片入面提到要贏就要記返個初心 <br />\n要記返6月7月香港人嗰份團結<br />\n記住場運動可以行到今時今日正正係因為不分化<br />\n和理非同勇武互相嘅尊重同體諒<br />\n<br />\n記住你哋自己係立法會入面寫嘅是你教我們和平遊行是沒用的<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人要團結先可以贏 唔好重犯2014嘅錯<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Fs3H2-5DHoo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFs3H2-5DHoo&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6Ij2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=f8ebfda7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Fs3H2-5DHoo</a>"},{"pid":"5b5544000958b83265bdebf32c6a46d92d0b01bb","tid":1816903,"uid":42281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:33:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1302e755ff1cb18ce871a53200a51e1539a95cdf","tid":1816903,"uid":42281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:33:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab8077b2f83d1a7efa9997e7d021f55e79e2829f","tid":1816903,"uid":343361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:34:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n只有同美國佬一齊武力升級<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"a3bdab40d0b922bbdec4d191b624ec761fc4046d","tid":1816903,"uid":42281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:34:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e7ec6b3003f9ae